# TestiFi Privacy Policy  
*Last Updated: November 4, 2025*

TestiFi (the “App”) is operated as a DBA. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect information when you use the App during its beta phase. By using TestiFi, you agree to this policy.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

### a. Information You Provide  
- **Testimony Content**: Everything you share in the chat (your personal story about your journey to knowing Christ) becomes part of your final testimony, which is **posted publicly**.  
- **No Account Required**: There is no sign-up, email, or username collected.

### b. Automatically Collected Information  
When you use the App, we collect:  
- IP address  
- Device type and operating system  
- App usage data (e.g., timestamps, interaction patterns)  

We use this solely to improve the beta version.

---

## 2. How We Use Your Information

| Purpose | Data Used |
|--------|-----------|
| Generate and publish your public testimony | Chat content |
| Provide text-to-speech (TTS) audio | Final testimony text |
| Store media files | TTS audio files |
| Debug and improve the App during beta | IP, device, usage logs, full chat transcripts |
| Process conversations via AI service | Full chat content (sent to Grok API for generating responses) |

**We do not sell, rent, or share your data for marketing.**  
**We do not use your data for advertising.**

---

## 3. How We Share Your Information

| Recipient | What Is Shared | Purpose |
|----------|----------------|--------|
| **Public Internet** | Final testimony + TTS audio | Core feature of the App |
| **Google Gemini** | Final testimony text | Generate TTS audio |
| **Backblaze B2** | TTS audio files | Secure media storage |
| **xAI (Grok API)** | Full chat content and prompts | Power the conversational AI responses during your session |
| **Internal Team** | All beta data (chats, logs) | Quality control & development |

**Note on Grok API**: Your conversations are sent through the Grok API provided by xAI. For details on how xAI handles this data, please review their [Enterprise Privacy Policy](https://x.ai/legal/privacy-policy) and [Enterprise FAQs](https://x.ai/legal/faq-enterprise). xAI does not use API inputs/outputs for model training by default, and data is deleted within 30 days unless required otherwise.

---

## 4. Public Nature of Testimonies

- Your finished testimony (text + audio) will be **publicly viewable** by anyone with the link or on the App’s public gallery.  
- **Do NOT include real names, locations, contact info, or any other PII** you want kept private.  
- Once published, testimonies **cannot be edited or removed** during beta.

---


## 5. Data Retention & Deletion

- **Beta Data**: All chats, logs, and usage data will be **permanently deleted** once beta testing ends and the App launches publicly.  
- **Public Testimonies**: Remain online indefinitely (unless the entire service shuts down).  
- **Grok API Data**: Handled per xAI's retention policy (typically 30 days for inputs/outputs).

---

## 6. Children’s Privacy

The App is available to all ages. However:  
- **We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.**  
- Parents: if your child submits a testimony, it will be public. Review their story before submission.

---

## 7. Your Choices

- **Avoid PII**: Simply omit sensitive details from your story.  
- **Stop Using the App**: Uninstall to prevent further data collection.  
- **Data Access/Deletion (Beta Only)**: Email **privacy@testifi.app** with your IP address or approximate usage time; we’ll locate and delete your beta records early.

---

## 8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy during beta. Material changes will be announced in the App. Continued use after changes means you accept the new terms.

---

## 9. Contact Us

Questions, concerns, or data requests?  
Email: **privacy@testifi.app**

---

*This policy is provided for the beta phase only. A final version will be published at launch.*
